# Tools

<!-- 中文注释：本节列出项目中可用的 Python 工具，以及在不同场景下的使用方式。 -->

Note all the tools are in python3. So in the case you need to do batch processing, you can always consult the python files and write your own script.

<!-- 中文注释：所有工具都基于 Python 3；如果需要批处理，可以阅读这些 Python 文件并编写自己的脚本。 -->

## Screenshot Verification

<!-- 中文注释：截图验证工具用于抓取网页截图，并借助 LLM 检查页面视觉效果。 -->

The screenshot verification workflow allows you to capture screenshots of web pages and verify their appearance using LLMs. The following tools are available:

1. Screenshot Capture:

<!-- 中文注释：截图采集命令；可传入 URL、输出路径以及截图宽高。 -->

```bash
venv/bin/python3 tools/screenshot_utils.py URL [--output OUTPUT] [--width WIDTH] [--height HEIGHT]
```

2. LLM Verification with Images:

<!-- 中文注释：图片验证命令；把截图和验证问题发送给指定 LLM 提供商。 -->

```bash
venv/bin/python3 tools/llm_api.py --prompt "Your verification question" --provider {openai|anthropic} --image path/to/screenshot.png
```

Example workflow:

<!-- 中文注释：下面展示如何在 Python 中先截图，再调用 LLM 询问页面视觉信息。 -->

```python
from screenshot_utils import take_screenshot_sync
from llm_api import query_llm

# Take a screenshot
# 中文注释：截取指定网页并保存为本地图片。

screenshot_path = take_screenshot_sync('https://example.com', 'screenshot.png')

# Verify with LLM
# 中文注释：把截图交给 LLM，询问页面背景色和标题等视觉信息。

response = query_llm(
    "What is the background color and title of this webpage?",
    provider="openai",  # or "anthropic"
    image_path=screenshot_path
)
print(response)
```

## LLM

<!-- 中文注释：本节说明如何调用项目内封装的 LLM 工具。 -->

You always have an LLM at your side to help you with the task. For simple tasks, you could invoke the LLM by running the following command:

<!-- 中文注释：简单问题可以直接通过命令行调用 `tools/llm_api.py`。 -->

```
venv/bin/python3 ./tools/llm_api.py --prompt "What is the capital of France?" --provider "anthropic"
```

The LLM API supports multiple providers:

<!-- 中文注释：以下是当前 LLM API 支持的模型服务商与默认模型说明。 -->

- OpenAI (default, model: gpt-4o)
- Azure OpenAI (model: configured via AZURE_OPENAI_MODEL_DEPLOYMENT in .env file, defaults to gpt-4o-ms)
- DeepSeek (model: deepseek-chat)
- Anthropic (model: claude-3-sonnet-20240229)
- Gemini (model: gemini-pro)
- Local LLM (model: Qwen/Qwen2.5-32B-Instruct-AWQ)

But usually its a better idea to check the content of the file and use the APIs in the `tools/llm_api.py` file to invoke the LLM if needed.

<!-- 中文注释：通常建议先阅读 `tools/llm_api.py` 的实现，再按实际需要调用对应 API。 -->

## Web browser

<!-- 中文注释：本节说明如何使用网页抓取工具读取网页内容。 -->

You could use the `tools/web_scraper.py` file to scrape the web.

<!-- 中文注释：下面命令可并发抓取多个 URL 的网页内容，`--max-concurrent` 控制并发数。 -->

```bash
venv/bin/python3 ./tools/web_scraper.py --max-concurrent 3 URL1 URL2 URL3
```
This will output the content of the web pages.

<!-- 中文注释：命令执行后会输出目标网页的正文内容。 -->

## Search engine

<!-- 中文注释：本节说明如何使用项目内搜索引擎工具查询网络结果。 -->

You could use the `tools/search_engine.py` file to search the web.

<!-- 中文注释：将搜索关键词作为参数传入即可获取搜索结果。 -->

```bash
venv/bin/python3 ./tools/search_engine.py "your search keywords"
```
This will output the search results in the following format:

<!-- 中文注释：搜索结果会包含 URL、标题和摘要，格式如下。 -->

```
URL: https://example.com
Title: This is the title of the search result
Snippet: This is a snippet of the search result
```
If needed, you can further use the `web_scraper.py` file to scrape the web page content.

<!-- 中文注释：如果搜索摘要不够，可以继续用 `web_scraper.py` 抓取具体页面内容。 -->

# Lessons

<!-- 中文注释：本节记录长期有效的经验教训，分为用户指定规则和 Cursor 自动学习到的规则。 -->

## User Specified Lessons

<!-- 中文注释：用户明确要求遵守的项目习惯，应优先执行。 -->

- You have a python venv in ./venv. Always use (activate) it when doing python development. First, to check whether 'uv' is available, use `which uv`. If that's the case, first activate the venv, and then use `uv pip install` to install packages. Otherwise, fall back to `pip`.
  <!-- 中文注释：做 Python 开发时优先使用 `./venv` 虚拟环境；如果存在 `uv`，激活环境后用 `uv pip install`，否则使用 `pip`。 -->
- Due to Cursor's limit, when you use `git` and `gh` and need to submit a multiline commit message, first write the message in a file, and then use `git commit -F <filename>` or similar command to commit. And then remove the file. Include "[Cursor] " in the commit message and PR title.
  <!-- 中文注释：提交多行 git/gh 信息时，先写入临时文件，再用 `git commit -F` 等方式提交；提交信息和 PR 标题要包含 `[Cursor] ` 前缀。 -->

## Cursor learned

<!-- 中文注释：这里记录 Cursor 在项目过程中总结出的注意事项。 -->

- For search results, ensure proper handling of different character encodings (UTF-8) for international queries
  <!-- 中文注释：处理国际化搜索结果时，要注意 UTF-8 等字符编码问题。 -->
- When using seaborn styles in matplotlib, use 'seaborn-v0_8' instead of 'seaborn' as the style name due to recent seaborn version changes
  <!-- 中文注释：新版 seaborn/matplotlib 样式名应使用 `seaborn-v0_8`，不要使用旧的 `seaborn`。 -->
- Use 'gpt-4o' as the model name for OpenAI's GPT-4 with vision capabilities
  <!-- 中文注释：调用具备视觉能力的 OpenAI GPT-4 时，模型名使用 `gpt-4o`。 -->
- When searching for recent news, use the current year (2025) instead of previous years, or simply use the "recent" keyword to get the latest information
  <!-- 中文注释：搜索最新新闻时，要使用当前年份或 `recent` 等关键词来提高时效性。 -->

